WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: _k2_hAE8PQg

NOTE Language: en

00:00:08.520 --> 00:00:14.200
Today we are going to celebrate

00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:25.360
the Puja of Gauri.

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:32.840
She came on this earth

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:39.600
many-a-times to kill the people

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:45.400
who were doing wrong things,

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:51.920
who were trying to kill good people.

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:57.640
She has done Her level to do that,

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:05.680
and today we are celebrating Her birthday.

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.440
You all know so much about it

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:16.400
that I need not tell you,

00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:23.200
but what you have to know is that

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:33.040
She came on this earth to save you

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:38.960
from all kinds of troubles.

00:01:40.080 --> 00:01:43.600
For Her you were important, very important,

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:48.720
because you were doing Devi Puja.

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:56.240
And so we are celebrating today this Devi Puja,

00:01:57.160 --> 00:01:59.800
with all our heart,

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:05.560
because whatever ill people did to you,

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:09.360
She came to destroy them.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:16.960
So today is a very great day for you to thank Her,

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:23.520
thank Her for Her protection and

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:30.440
for Her understanding

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:37.040
as to what you have been tortured for.

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:49.640
I'm happy you are all here to celebrate Her birthday,

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:56.360
and to be surrendered to Her

00:02:56.960 --> 00:03:00.640
so that She can always,

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:04.960
always protect you

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:08.080
and give you Her blessings.

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:15.160
So may God bless you all,

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:17.600
your children,

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:20.400
your families,

00:03:20.600 --> 00:03:26.240
and that you bring great joy and protection.

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:43.160
It's very kind of you to have come today, so far away.

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:48.440
I'm very happy to see you.

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:54.160
Moreover, you have got tomorrow also

00:03:55.120 --> 00:04:00.400
that you can celebrate.

00:04:07.160 --> 00:04:13.400
Today we are not going to have any questions and solutions;

00:04:13.600 --> 00:04:18.760
we are just going to worship the Goddess, that's all,

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:24.920
and request Her to protect us

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:30.560
from all kinds of problems that are facing us.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:34.120
Thank you very much.
